<Layout>
  <section class="faq-section">
    <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
    <p class="sub">Still wondering how things work? Here are answers to some common questions.</p>

    <div class="faq-list">
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What is the JNVCKM Alumni Association?</summary>
        <p>
          It's a registered group of former students from Jawahar Navodaya Vidyalaya, Chikmagalur. The association helps connect alumni and contributes to both the school and society.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Who can join the alumni group?</summary>
        <p>
          Any former student of JNVCKM is welcome. Whether you graduated recently or decades ago, you're part of the family.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Is there a membership fee?</summary>
        <p>
          Currently, there's no fee to join. Donations are appreciated to support events and contributions.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How can I contribute or volunteer?</summary>
        <p>
          You can reach out through the website or join our WhatsApp and Telegram groups. Every bit of help countsâ€”whether it's time, skills, or funds.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How often are events held?</summary>
        <p>
          Reunions and meetups are planned based on regional convenience and interest. Follow our site or socials to stay updated.
        </p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>